Package com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.listener

Provides interfaces and classes used to register callbacks and event listeners of life cycle of native instances.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AttachCallback Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when attached to native memory.
AttachCopyCallback Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when attaching a non-native (detached) copy.
AttachCopyLifecycleListener This interface is implemented by listeners to be notified of attach copy events.
AttachLifecycleListener This interface is implemented by listeners to be notified of attach events.
DetachCallback Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when detached from native memory.
DetachCopyCallback Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when creating a detached (non-native) clone.
DetachCopyLifecycleListener This interface is implemented by listeners to be notified of detach copy events.
DetachLifecycleListener This interface is implemented by listeners to be notified of detach events.
FetchCallback Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when fetched from native memory.
FetchLifecycleListener Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when fetching from native memory.
InstanceLifecycleListener All lifecycle listeners extend from this base interface.
MakeNativeCallback Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when made native "unfetching" to native memory.
MakeNativeLifecycleListener This interface is implemented by listeners to be notified of make native events.
UnFetchCallback Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when "unfetched" to native memory.
UnFetchLifecycleListener Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when "unfetching" to native memory.
 

Class Summary
AttachCopyLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in attach copy life cycle event notifications.
AttachLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in attach life cycle event notifications.
DetachCopyLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in detach copy life cycle event notifications.
DetachLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in detach life cycle event notifications.
FetchLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in fetch life cycle event notifications.
InstanceLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in life cycle event notifications.
MakeNativeLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in make native life cycle event notifications.
UnFetchLifecycleEvent This is the event class used in "unfetch" life cycle event notifications.
 

Package com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.listener Description

Provides interfaces and classes used to register callbacks and event listeners of life cycle of native instances.
